text:
[Verse]
Lights flashing bright
Feet moving fast
Feel the beat now
Make the night last

[Verse 2]
Hands in the air
Lost in the sound
No time to spare
As we spin round

[Chorus]
Dancing through the night
Shining stars so bright
Feel the rhythm right
Keep it going till light

[Verse 3]
Hearts beating strong
Music so loud
This is our song
You're my night crowd

[Bridge]
Don't stop the flow
Under moon's glow
Together we go
Rhythms that grow

[Chorus]
Dancing through the night
Shining stars so bright
Feel the rhythm right
Keep it going till light
title: Dancing Through the Night
